data.description: This modern 4-bedroom, 2-bath home, built in 2017, offers 10 ft ceilings, granite countertops, trey ceilings, a wood-burning fireplace, Double walk in closets, and a soaker tub for the ultimate relaxation. A spacious two-car garage and a large backyard provide ample space for both storage and leisure. Nestled in a vibrant community, this home offers convenient access to local amenities, including grocery stores like Publix, dining options from fast food to sit-down restaurants, and a nearby Starbucks. With close proximity to Redstone Arsenal, this property is Great for those seeking a blend of comfort and convenience in a family-friendly neighborhood. Just minutes to Town Madison
